race.comment: JUNK YARD LORAIN (3) was a last start winner (17.50) at this track in a Maiden and will jump from box 3 for the first time. Will go close again if runs up to latest. KNOX GORGE (2) jumped from this same draw and was close to the lead throughout before boxing on well and holding a 6 length third (23.11) at this track over 400m in a Novice race. Worth following up. MISS DAISY DUKE (1) had to overcome a collision with another runner and could manage only a distant sixth (18.01) in a Novice race over 300m at this track. Better than last start and can bounce back. PLAYGROUND BULLY (4) was a shade disappointing when in the placings as favourite last start â€“ worth including.
